msgid ""
"[MIT; now rare] Having the quality of a :ref:`bagbiter`\\. \"This bagbiting "
"system won't let me compute the factorial of a negative number.\" Compare "
":ref:`losing`\\, :ref:`cretinous`\\, :ref:`bletcherous`\\, barfucious (under"
" :ref:`barfulous`\\) and chomping (under :ref:`chomp`\\)."
msgstr ""
"[MIT。今はまれ]\\ :ref:`bagbiter`\\ "
"の性質を持つこと。「このbagbitingなシステムは負の数の階乗を計算させてくれない」。\\ :ref:`losing`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`cretinous`\\ 、\\ :ref:`bletcherous`\\ 、barfucious(\\ "
":ref:`barfulous`\\ の項)、chomping(\\ :ref:`chomp`\\ の項)と比較せよ。"
